  "detailed_description": "<h1>Follow us on X</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >50 choices in the adventure will test your true personality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you a Paladin who protects the weak, or a cold and selfish assassin for hire?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover your exact personality type through the Alignment chart and Personality Tags.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/9b48e5617cd56f8f6e711158ea126b8d.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/9b48e5617cd56f8f6e711158ea126b8d.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/9b48e5617cd56f8f6e711158ea126b8d.mp4?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players utilize slashing as a core mechanic to disable monster attacks and to solve certain puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/c2c5970616f783bc3b89990d16082c04.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/c2c5970616f783bc3b89990d16082c04.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/c2c5970616f783bc3b89990d16082c04.mp4?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your choices shape the story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your decisions may not only result in the deaths of certain key characters but also lead to your demise by being crushed by boulders, Earth's gravity, assassination, or being eaten alive, among other possibilities...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/2f2f4fc19314cae35c165c1dc1aca1b0.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/2f2f4fc19314cae35c165c1dc1aca1b0.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/2f2f4fc19314cae35c165c1dc1aca1b0.mp4?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Returning to the golden age of 90s video games</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Apocalypse Sacrifice is a blend of 90s retro style and modern game design. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its classic adventure gameplay allows you to experience nostalgic emotions while also providing a fresh gaming experience </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/89ee7dc0409e77482d316422784aadd3.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/89ee7dc0409e77482d316422784aadd3.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse scenes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From forests to deserts, from modern buildings to ancient ruins, from the future to the past. <br>Travel across different times and spaces.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventurers should always keep adventuring! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/a7e85682ed2d80c50139a6d0b9e0d939.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/a7e85682ed2d80c50139a6d0b9e0d939.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/a7e85682ed2d80c50139a6d0b9e0d939.mp4?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Digging for the truth </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully read NPC dialogues, gather items, documents, and records scattered throughout the world, and piece together the truth. Don't let any one-sided statements influence your judgment!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >50 choices in the adventure will test your true personality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you a Paladin who protects the weak, or a cold and selfish assassin for hire?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover your exact personality type through the Alignment chart and Personality Tags.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/9b48e5617cd56f8f6e711158ea126b8d.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/9b48e5617cd56f8f6e711158ea126b8d.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/9b48e5617cd56f8f6e711158ea126b8d.mp4?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players utilize slashing as a core mechanic to disable monster attacks and to solve certain puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/c2c5970616f783bc3b89990d16082c04.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/c2c5970616f783bc3b89990d16082c04.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/c2c5970616f783bc3b89990d16082c04.mp4?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your choices shape the story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your decisions may not only result in the deaths of certain key characters but also lead to your demise by being crushed by boulders, Earth's gravity, assassination, or being eaten alive, among other possibilities...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/2f2f4fc19314cae35c165c1dc1aca1b0.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/2f2f4fc19314cae35c165c1dc1aca1b0.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/2f2f4fc19314cae35c165c1dc1aca1b0.mp4?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Returning to the golden age of 90s video games</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Apocalypse Sacrifice is a blend of 90s retro style and modern game design. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its classic adventure gameplay allows you to experience nostalgic emotions while also providing a fresh gaming experience </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/89ee7dc0409e77482d316422784aadd3.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/89ee7dc0409e77482d316422784aadd3.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse scenes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From forests to deserts, from modern buildings to ancient ruins, from the future to the past. <br>Travel across different times and spaces.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventurers should always keep adventuring! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/a7e85682ed2d80c50139a6d0b9e0d939.poster.avif?t=1732779426\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/a7e85682ed2d80c50139a6d0b9e0d939.webm?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776600/extras/a7e85682ed2d80c50139a6d0b9e0d939.mp4?t=1732779426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Digging for the truth </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully read NPC dialogues, gather items, documents, and records scattered throughout the world, and piece together the truth. Don't let any one-sided statements influence your judgment!</p>",
